{"_path":"/maps/_ai/models/optimization","_dir":"models","_draft":false,"_partial":true,"_locale":"","title":"Optimization","description":"Model optimization techniques","original_path":"_ai/optimization.md","body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h1","props":{"id":"优化-optimization"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"优化 (Optimization)"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"flash-attention内存高效的注意力计算"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Flash Attention：内存高效的注意力计算"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Flash Attention 由 Tri Dao 开发，通过分块计算（tiling）和重计算（recomputation）策略，将注意力计算从 O(N²) 内存复杂度降至 O(N)，同时保持计算精度不变。Flash Attention-3 进一步优化 Hopper GPU，利用 Tensor Core 异步执行，支持 2-4 倍更长序列，实际计算速度提升 2-4 倍。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"见："},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://github.com/Dao-AILab/flash-attention","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Flash Attention GitHub"}]},{"type":"text","value":" | "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://tridao.me/blog/2024/flash3/","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Flash Attention-3 博客"}]},{"type":"text","value":" | "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://arxiv.org/abs/2205.14135","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Flash Attention 论文"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"bitsandbytes8-bit4-bit-量化训练"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"bitsandbytes：8-bit/4-bit 量化训练"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"bitsandbytes 是 Hugging Face 生态的量化训练库，提供 8-bit AdamW、4-bit 量化训练等功能。与 PEFT 结合实现 QLoRA——4-bit 量化基础模型权重，冻结量化权重，训练 LoRA 适配器，训练时动态反量化，推理时保持量化。让 7B 模型能在消费级 GPU（如 RTX 3090）上微调。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"见："},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://github.com/bitsandbytes-foundation/bitsandbytes","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"bitsandbytes GitHub"}]},{"type":"text","value":" | "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://arxiv.org/abs/2305.14314","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"QLoRA 论文"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"gptq训练后-int4-量化"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"GPTQ：训练后 INT4 量化"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"GPTQ 是训练后量化（PTQ）方法，通过逐层量化并补偿误差，将模型压缩至 INT4 精度。适合部署场景，无需重新训练。广泛应用于 llama.cpp、Ollama 等本地推理框架，可在单卡加载 2-3 倍大的模型。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"见："},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://arxiv.org/abs/2210.17323","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"GPTQ 论文"}]},{"type":"text","value":" | "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://www.newline.co/@zaoyang/gptq-vs-awq-quantization--d792476e","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"GPTQ vs AWQ 对比"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"awq激活感知权重量化"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"AWQ：激活感知权重量化"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"AWQ（Activation-aware Weight Quantization）发现\"并非所有权重的贡献相同\"——保护对激活值影响大的权重通道，可以显著减少量化损失。相比 GPTQ，perplexity 损失更小，支持 INT4 乘加指令，吞吐提升 2-3 倍，与 TensorRT-LLM、vLLM 集成良好。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"见："},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://arxiv.org/abs/2306.00978","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"AWQ 论文"}]},{"type":"text","value":" | "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://github.com/mit-han-lab/llm-awq","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"AWQ GitHub"}]},{"type":"text","value":" | "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://leimao.github.io/blog/AWQ-Activation-Aware-Weight-Quantization/","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"AWQ 深度解析"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"ggufllamacpp-本地推理格式"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"GGUF：llama.cpp 本地推理格式"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"GGUF（GPT-Generated Unified Format）是 llama.cpp 项目的模型格式，专为本地 CPU/GPU 推理优化。支持多种量化方案：Q4_0（极致压缩）、Q4_K_M（平衡选择）、Q5_K_M（质量优先）、Q8_0（接近无损）。是 Ollama、LM Studio 等本地 LLM 工具的标准格式。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"见："},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://github.com/ggerganov/ggml/blob/master/docs/gguf.md","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"GGUF 格式规范"}]},{"type":"text","value":" | "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://kaitchup.substack.com/p/choosing-a-gguf-model-k-quants-i","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"GGUF 量化选择指南"}]},{"type":"text","value":" | "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://arxiv.org/pdf/2601.14277","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"llama.cpp 量化论文"}]}]}],"toc":{"title":"","searchDepth":2,"depth":2,"links":[{"id":"flash-attention内存高效的注意力计算","depth":2,"text":"Flash Attention：内存高效的注意力计算"},{"id":"bitsandbytes8-bit4-bit-量化训练","depth":2,"text":"bitsandbytes：8-bit/4-bit 量化训练"},{"id":"gptq训练后-int4-量化","depth":2,"text":"GPTQ：训练后 INT4 量化"},{"id":"awq激活感知权重量化","depth":2,"text":"AWQ：激活感知权重量化"},{"id":"ggufllamacpp-本地推理格式","depth":2,"text":"GGUF：llama.cpp 本地推理格式"}]}},"_type":"markdown","_id":"content:6.maps:_ai:models:optimization.md","_source":"content","_file":"6.maps/_ai/models/optimization.md","_stem":"6.maps/_ai/models/optimization","_extension":"md"}